commit.message: Fixed update presence on client party reconnect

Fix ClientPartyMember meta race condition

Caused the client to not equip the meta if the client joined too fast

before_close in utility funcs improvements

- Renamed event_close() -> event_before_close() but an alias does still exist for the old name.
- Client.dispatch_and_wait_for() now can error without affecting anything

rename to PresenceGameplayStats.kills

Renamed .num_kills to .kills but added an alias for .num_kills as well.

Fix conn processing error in event_party_member_zombie()

Errored because it was processing connections before the party is None check

Better character muc nick char removal

- improved XMPPClient._remove_illegal_characters()
- fixed nick using display name twice instead of user id
Reconnect to party on auth refresh
